#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.231:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhussa vā bhikkhuniyā vā cakkhuviññeyyesu "
"rūpesu yo rāgo so natthi, yo doso so natthi, yo moho so natthi, yo rāgo so "
"pahīno, yo doso so pahīno, yo moho so pahīno, tassa adhimattā cepi "
"cakkhuviññeyyā rūpā cakkhussa āpāthaṃ āgacchanti nevassa cittaṃ "
"pariyādiyanti; ko pana vādo parittānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Take any monk or nun who, when it comes to sights known by the eye, has no "
"greed, hate, and delusion left, and has given them up. If even compelling "
"sights come into their range of vision they don’t overcome their mind, not "
"to mention those that are trivial."

msgctxt "sn35.231:8.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn35.231:8.3"
msgid ""
"Yo, bhikkhave, rāgo so natthi, yo doso so natthi, yo moho so natthi, yo rāgo "
"so pahīno, yo doso so pahīno, yo moho so pahīno … pe …."
msgstr ""
"Because they have no greed, hate, and delusion left, and have given them up."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi4.162"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.231:9.1"
msgid ""
"Yassa kassaci, bhikkhave, bhikkhussa vā bhikkhuniyā vā jivhāviññeyyesu "
"rasesu … pe … manoviññeyyesu dhammesu yo rāgo so natthi, yo doso so natthi, "
"yo moho so natthi, yo rāgo so pahīno, yo doso so pahīno, yo moho so pahīno, "
"tassa adhimattā cepi manoviññeyyā dhammā manassa āpāthaṃ āgacchanti nevassa "
"cittaṃ pariyādiyanti; ko pana vādo parittānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"When it comes to sounds … smells … tastes … touches … thoughts known by the "
