msgstr ""
"Because they have no greed, hate, and delusion left, and have given them up."

msgctxt "sn35.231:9.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, khīrarukkho assattho vā nigrodho vā pilakkho vā "
"udumbaro vā sukkho kolāpo terovassiko."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a latex-producing tree—such as a bodhi, a banyan, a wavy "
"leaf fig, or a cluster fig—that’s dried up, withered, and decrepit."

msgctxt "sn35.231:9.5"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ puriso tiṇhāya kuṭhāriyā yato yato ābhindeyya āgaccheyya khīran”ti?"
